Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.50,0:02:35.45,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an5\fs28\shad0}\N\N\N\N\N\N\N\N最前线
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.65,0:01:40.71,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,炮火全开 想办法压制住姆赛舰
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.61,0:01:44.75,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,3号舰被击沉
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.75,0:01:47.37,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,主炮向前方集中攻击 拦下那家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.37,0:01:49.80,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,速度太快了 来不及锁定
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.03,0:01:57.65,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,敌人的MA突破第3防卫线
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.65,0:01:59.65,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,从11马赫开始减速中
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.65,0:02:02.08,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,距到达贾布罗还剩9秒
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.82,0:02:43.08,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,贾布罗啊...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.88,0:02:45.50,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,模拟试验终了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.03,0:02:50.35,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,那么 敌人新型机的目的就是直接攻击联邦的本部了？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.45,0:02:50.90,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.40,0:02:53.60,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,从我们所得到的情报看来是的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.30,0:02:56.80,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,那就开始进行吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.80,0:02:57.46,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.76,0:03:01.22,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,搜索敌人基地并歼灭敌人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.72,0:03:03.20,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,对时
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.30,0:03:06.70,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,作战开始
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.70,0:03:21.70,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,突破大气层来袭的炮台
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.90,0:03:25.36,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,雷比尔的“南极条约”也不用遵守了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.36,0:03:27.00,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,大佐
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.80,0:03:31.27,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,对08小队的处置 那样就可以了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.35,0:03:33.12,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,那个少尉吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.12,0:03:37.92,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,与敌人机师相识的话 说不定可以利用这个机会
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.12,0:03:39.41,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,怎能用那种理由...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.11,0:03:43.10,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,没关系 已经上了保险了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.50,0:03:45.01,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,而且是双重的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.77,0:03:48.27,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,山达斯 有在听吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.27,0:03:50.09,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,啊... 是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.49,0:03:53.24,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,于ALPHA点降落后
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.54,0:03:56.95,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,一边搜索敌人基地一边向BETA点移动
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.15,0:03:59.62,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,与前来接应的美迪亚会合后返航
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.62,0:04:01.50,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,此外
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.50,0:04:05.15,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,本次作战的目的只是探查敌人基地
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.55,0:04:07.61,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,最优先考虑的是得到情报
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.01,0:04:09.59,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,尽量避免战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.29,0:04:14.03,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,也就是说 即使女朋友出现也不用与她战斗了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.93,0:04:16.20,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,女朋友？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.00,0:04:21.19,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,队长的？真的？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.19,0:04:24.44,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,什么嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.04,0:04:30.35,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,我住在野战医院里 却成天被迫去应付一群恶心的白衣天使
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.98,0:04:33.94,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,太狡猾了 这种“变脸”
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.04,0:04:37.74,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,还从容不迫的啊...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.50,0:04:40.45,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,我说啊 卡莲 我们也...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.65,0:04:41.85,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,艾历多亚
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.65,0:04:43.95,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.42,0:04:45.83,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,吵死了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.73,0:04:49.70,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,什么嘛 卡莲
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.70,0:04:51.80,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,太冷淡了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.80,0:04:55.60,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,第一次用降落伞空降 我可没闲工夫和你瞎搅和
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.53,0:04:59.42,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,别碰我 真烦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.92,0:05:00.60,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,队长...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.92,0:05:05.69,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,其实 我...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.89,0:05:07.78,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,离抵达空投地点还有5分钟
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.08,0:05:10.06,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,好 准备出击
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.26,0:05:11.30,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.30,0:05:12.62,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,没办法 走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.32,0:05:15.72,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,山达斯 有什么话要说吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.19,0:05:19.26,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,没什么...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.70,0:05:23.15,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,是么...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.12,0:05:26.50,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,那女朋友长得漂亮吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.61,0:05:27.84,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,不知道哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.44,0:05:30.30,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,哟 间谍老兄
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.98,0:05:32.40,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,保重哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.10,0:05:37.76,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,队长绝不是间谍 他不是那种卑鄙的人！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.26,0:05:40.48,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,废话少说了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.78,0:05:44.16,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,终点站到了 进棺材去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.96,0:05:46.83,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,山达斯 走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.60,0:05:54.74,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,检测完毕
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.64,0:06:01.37,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,启动顶端观景仪
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.37,0:06:04.14,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,照模拟演练去做就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.14,0:06:06.50,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,吉翁的女机师？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.50,0:06:08.38,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,多么的浪漫啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.58,0:06:09.80,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,悲情之恋呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.05,0:06:14.60,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,队长他... 绝不是间谍
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.43,0:06:32.43,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么会这样！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.83,0:06:33.82,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,队长
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.82,0:06:35.52,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,我进入了与水牛级的遭遇战！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.72,0:06:37.03,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,卡莲没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.63,0:06:39.10,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,赶快弹射出去！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.10,0:06:42.29,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,稍等一下 现在让你出去的话这里会失去平衡
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.49,0:06:44.61,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,请快一点
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.73,0:06:51.98,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,卡莲 别停下快行动
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.35,0:06:54.44,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,卡莲！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.04,0:06:56.72,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,亲爱的... 现在就来了...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.71,0:07:06.23,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,机身上方有机影
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.33,0:07:07.83,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,是正面 快开火
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.43,0:07:27.44,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.74,0:07:31.10,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,马上停止射击 不然就将你们击落
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.06,0:07:41.08,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,想这样同归于尽吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.47,0:07:53.42,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,第2引擎起火了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.62,0:07:54.92,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,快去灭火
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.92,0:07:57.89,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,各炮台停止射击
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.89,0:08:00.69,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,已经移至射程之外了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.10,0:08:09.04,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,要射击吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.74,0:08:12.51,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,不用了 先进行修理
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.21,0:08:15.20,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.55,0:08:24.96,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,剩下的人还没到吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.96,0:08:27.50,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,因为那台水牛级一边的引擎受损了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.12,0:08:31.76,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,发现类似水牛级的机影 与预定的航线不同
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.36,0:08:33.72,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,有没有联邦的机影
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.02,0:08:37.09,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,没有 但是它正冒着烟
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.59,0:08:39.39,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,加强防卫线的戒备
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.79,0:08:43.57,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,但愿只是引擎受损了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.11,0:08:56.40,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,130
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.40,0:08:57.39,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,120
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.39,0:08:58.26,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,110
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.26,0:08:59.31,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,喷射
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.35,0:09:07.76,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,完成着陆
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.95,0:09:18.50,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,真美啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.50,0:09:21.73,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,卡莲 没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.53,0:09:26.90,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,现在可不是赞美风景的时候吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.20,0:09:29.42,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,人家难得...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.27,0:09:32.55,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,在对岸？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.85,0:09:34.87,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,在哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.07,0:09:39.05,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,从水中！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.47,0:09:43.86,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,卡莲！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.33,0:10:07.32,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,卡莲你怎么能死啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.24,0:10:10.51,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,米凯尔 用汽垫车引开它
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.81,0:10:12.64,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,我一个人没法用机枪攻击的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.64,0:10:14.40,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,我的卡莲就能死的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.40,0:10:15.91,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么这样...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.61,0:10:18.07,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,拜托了 快点
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.70,0:10:40.66,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,卡莲 没受伤吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.96,0:10:43.20,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,回答我
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.37,0:10:45.70,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,艾历多亚...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.29,0:10:49.87,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,还能操纵吗 米凯尔有危险
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.07,0:10:52.42,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,可是显示器和瞄准仪都...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.42,0:10:54.50,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,没时间了 按我的指示做
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.91,0:10:57.40,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,由我来校准光束步枪
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.21,0:11:01.70,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,举高它
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.50,0:11:05.92,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,低一点
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.82,0:11:07.49,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,停
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.83,0:11:13.00,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,被它看到了 快点射击
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.30,0:11:17.68,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,向右修正6度 过来了...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.78,0:11:20.30,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,射击 射击~
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.89,0:11:30.37,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,艾历多亚？艾历多亚！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.29,0:11:45.30,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,艾历多亚
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.60,0:11:50.85,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,没受伤吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.50,0:11:53.74,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,艾历多亚
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.32,0:11:57.97,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,好像有点紧张过头了 曹长你呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.93,0:12:01.35,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,多亏有你我才得救了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.55,0:12:05.91,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,你死了的话我的人生计划可就乱掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.96,0:12:22.54,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,损失了大半物资和兵员14名
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.54,0:12:24.02,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,十分抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.02,0:12:24.85,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.85,0:12:28.79,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,用一边引擎受损的水牛级还要强行作战 是我的过失
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.19,0:12:30.29,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.49,0:12:32.33,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢您
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.73,0:12:34.65,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,你做得很好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.95,0:12:39.00,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,好 开工了 这些烟会被狗闻到的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.30,0:12:41.35,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,就算联邦再怎样愚蠢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.14,0:12:45.98,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,司令
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.38,0:12:50.50,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,请把这家伙借给我
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.23,0:12:52.70,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,那堆废铁？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.15,0:12:55.90,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,你不会是想寻死吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.30,0:12:59.05,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,想为主力部队的撤退争取点时间
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.39,0:13:02.50,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,和联邦的“有脸机”也有点恩怨要解决
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.17,0:13:07.50,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,向我保证活着回来的话...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.15,0:13:09.50,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,一定
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.62,0:13:12.96,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,我 一起去
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.96,0:13:14.16,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,我也是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.16,0:13:17.33,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,支援和补给都无法保障的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.33,0:13:19.03,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,我们心知
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.03,0:13:20.96,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,士兵们就拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.96,0:13:23.08,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,送他们上宇宙去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.68,0:13:25.20,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,你们...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.54,0:13:29.50,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,好 马杰拉特攻队 出击！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.50,0:13:30.50,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.98,0:13:34.57,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,别那么生气了 原谅我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.67,0:13:37.80,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,光束步枪的摄像仪接驳完毕
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.90,0:13:40.50,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,瞄准仪有影像了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.98,0:13:44.87,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,拿到曲子的版税后我会请你吃饭的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.07,0:13:48.30,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,大家听着
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.40,0:13:50.02,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,更改作战
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.72,0:13:53.52,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,卡莲和汽垫车继续前往会合地点
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.62,0:13:56.14,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,我和山达斯继续执行任务
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.24,0:13:59.32,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,发生战斗的话可就没什么把握了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.42,0:14:00.91,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,到那时就什么也别管
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.01,0:14:02.11,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,全力逃跑
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.21,0:14:04.80,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,那也算是作战吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.90,0:14:05.80,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.90,0:14:09.13,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,使出最新型MS的全部能力
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.23,0:14:10.73,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,拼命逃跑
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.53,0:14:24.46,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,要您帮忙真是抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.72,0:14:28.05,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,别客气 要是药品的话 我很乐意帮忙
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.05,0:14:29.34,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢您的帮助
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.04,0:14:31.84,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,我来帮忙
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.84,0:14:34.82,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,没关系的 请去休息吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.82,0:14:38.08,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,我来帮忙
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.96,0:14:52.66,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,这... 用这种药
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.66,0:14:54.65,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.55,0:14:57.68,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,这也算是医生的所为吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.28,0:15:02.10,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,为了完成APSARAS 这也是不得已的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.30,0:15:05.11,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,是哥哥下的命令吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.31,0:15:07.57,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,不 是我决定的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.07,0:15:10.37,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,身为医生的我受到良心的谴责
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.37,0:15:17.62,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 我们是赞成殖民地独立而参加了这场战争的职业军人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.93,0:15:21.83,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,利用APSARAS摧毁敌人总部
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.13,0:15:27.61,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,深信那才是身为军人现在最该做的事
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.85,0:15:31.66,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,必须得阻止 竟然无视中止命令
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.69,0:15:37.67,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,将RICK DOM用作发电机好像进行得挺顺利
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.67,0:15:39.10,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,当然
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.70,0:15:43.19,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,将7、8、9阶段都省略掉 加快作业
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.79,0:15:46.60,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,尤里阁下请求支援
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.80,0:15:47.60,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,支援？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.20,0:15:51.15,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,冒着暴露基地位置的危险吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.45,0:15:54.01,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,可总不能对同胞置之不理啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.91,0:15:58.10,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,那家伙也该学着自己照顾自己
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.40,0:16:03.83,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 想到从奥迪沙历尽苦难逃亡来的士兵们的心情...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.13,0:16:04.96,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,真没出息
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.46,0:16:08.54,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,没有比完成APSARAS更重要的责任了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.74,0:16:13.45,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶 混蛋基尼亚斯 竟然弃友军于不顾
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.14,0:16:20.36,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,无论如何 都要把他们送到宇宙去
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.36,0:16:23.12,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,拜托了 马杰拉特攻队
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.07,0:16:33.05,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,队长
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.45,0:16:34.63,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,敌人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.33,0:16:39.03,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,差不多是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.83,0:16:42.32,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,我是奉命监视队长的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.22,0:16:46.70,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,只因我老是违反军纪呀
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.20,0:16:48.98,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,别放在心上 山达斯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.78,0:16:54.72,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,小岛大队长也太过于担心了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.32,0:16:59.56,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,其实那是雷亚大佐的命令
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.55,0:17:04.81,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,那个人吗...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.90,0:17:10.99,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,审问会上也只有他接受我的申诉
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.19,0:17:12.56,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,启动地雷
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.86,0:17:15.78,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,但他其实并不相信我
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.69,0:17:19.70,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,右前方曾是战场 有多处金属反应
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.89,0:17:21.73,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,很适合设陷阱啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.40,0:17:23.80,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,退回到森林里
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.37,0:17:27.56,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,山达斯 撤退
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.46,0:17:30.96,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,机会来了 对准“有角机” 射击
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.60,0:17:37.80,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,不断射击 给“有角机”最后一击
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.95,0:17:38.89,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,射击
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.61,0:17:41.60,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,撤退
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.06,0:17:43.98,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,山达斯！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.19,0:17:50.75,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,别放松
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.75,0:17:52.61,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,将他们逐个击破
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.39,0:17:59.17,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,被锁定了 撤退
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.36,0:18:03.70,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,光学感应器被...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.47,0:18:10.87,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,巴利 鲁内 A阵型
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.07,0:18:14.50,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,烟雾散开之时就一决胜负
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.80,0:18:16.89,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,要利用心理战
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.09,0:18:18.57,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,联邦的MS
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.57,0:18:21.40,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,那个声音是... 之前的那个舰长
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.40,0:18:23.17,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,我叫波恩·阿姆思特
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.07,0:18:27.63,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,我来问你 为何那时不击落我们
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.13,0:18:28.93,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.03,0:18:31.92,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,我替士兵们谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.32,0:18:34.07,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,但我无法认同
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.57,0:18:35.90,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,我们是吉翁
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.90,0:18:38.78,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,绝不能接受联邦的同情
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.95,0:18:41.10,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,我只是不想有无谓的牺牲...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.30,0:18:43.48,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,想用那光束枪来杀死我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.77,0:18:47.10,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,果然如此
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.21,0:18:54.25,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,士兵们已疲惫不堪了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.25,0:18:56.76,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,请立即中止开发
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.91,0:19:02.70,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,那样又如何？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.50,0:19:06.61,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,你有办法中止这场战争吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.81,0:19:08.47,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,那种事怎么...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.67,0:19:12.84,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 应该已经下达了中止开发的命令
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.94,0:19:15.82,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,再强行使用药物也是无意义的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.82,0:19:18.16,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,真让人感动
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.86,0:19:21.11,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,我们可是在进行战争啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.41,0:19:23.90,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,APSARAS是一定要完成的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.24,0:19:27.60,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,我会把命令解除给你看的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.45,0:19:31.40,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,快点
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.80,0:19:33.11,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,司令也进去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.51,0:19:35.12,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,别说傻话了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.27,0:19:37.50,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,他们没回来前我怎么可以进去
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.13,0:19:43.06,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,队长
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.46,0:19:44.50,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.50,0:19:48.24,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,右边的脚被打坏 无法掩护你了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.44,0:19:50.54,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,流了很多血吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.74,0:19:53.11,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,不 我是说MS
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.88,0:19:58.05,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,我忘了1件重要的事...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.81,0:20:00.80,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,你能开枪吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.01,0:20:01.60,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,行！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.41,0:20:08.50,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,听着 就此撤退
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.70,0:20:11.38,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,都已经到这里了 别急着送死
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.68,0:20:12.97,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,已经争取到时间了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.95,0:20:18.56,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,好 逃跑这种事就交给我们来干吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.56,0:20:21.82,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,从奥迪沙来到这里一直都在逃跑呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.92,0:20:26.88,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,好 该决胜负了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.78,0:20:29.45,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,我并不是为了联邦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.65,0:20:30.87,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,而是...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.07,0:20:33.69,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,为了同伴而战！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.19,0:20:37.40,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,事到如今还说这些 别说傻话了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.62,0:21:21.50,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,我们回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.03,0:21:25.03,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,还是输了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.93,0:21:31.80,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,能回来就好 真的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.80,0:21:34.74,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,主力部队呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.94,0:21:36.95,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,多亏你们 已经全都进去了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.45,0:21:40.02,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,这样就能回宇宙去了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.22,0:21:43.06,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,胖子还是喜欢无重力状态吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.80,0:21:45.50,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,真过分啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.50,0:21:47.36,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,嘿 别生气
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.50,0:21:50.60,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.60,0:21:51.90,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,发生什么事了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.46,0:21:58.38,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,尤里·凯拉尼少将
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.58,0:22:00.23,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,开门 基尼亚斯
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.23,0:22:03.19,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,详细情形 我已全部从你的秘书官那里打听到了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.99,0:22:05.92,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,你对辛西娅做了什么！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.52,0:22:09.91,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,中止命令还没有递交给基尼阁下
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.49,0:22:13.83,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,您战死的话
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.83,0:22:16.83,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,命令就永远送不到本国了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.93,0:22:19.81,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,快逃 逃出矿坑
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.01,0:22:24.39,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,少将光荣地战死了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.39,0:22:29.19,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,鲁内 巴利
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.69,0:22:33.50,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,基尼亚斯！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.70,0:22:37.25,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯？怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.75,0:24:23.05,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,联邦在探明了敌人基地之后 终于发起了总攻
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.75,0:24:27.41,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,突然出现在我们面前的蓝色MS
Dialogue: 0,0:24:28.38,0:24:31.50,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,仅他一个就能愚弄3台GUNDAM的那个家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:24:31.50,0:24:32.45,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,是王牌！
Dialogue: 0,0:24:33.13,0:24:35.05,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,同伴们一个接一个地倒下了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:35.35,0:24:36.20,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,接着...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:37.10,0:24:39.45,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,我... 会死吗
Dialogue: 0,0:24:40.75,0:24:41.95,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,赢了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:43.20,0:24:44.05,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,下回
Dialogue: 0,0:24:44.05,0:24:46.07,Chinese,NTP,0,0,0,,震动的山(前篇)
